1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,271
Good agent work does not begin with a blank prompt.

2
00:00:03,221 --> 00:00:09,403
It begins with real materials and a concrete artifact that another person can inspect, edit, and continue.

3
00:00:09,403 --> 00:00:14,048
First, define the artifact and provide the smallest complete source package.

4
00:00:14,048 --> 00:00:19,750
Second, make constraints, review expectations, and destination format observable.

5
00:00:19,750 --> 00:00:25,570
Third, return a review-ready first version with evidence, open questions, and a clear handoff.

6
00:00:25,570 --> 00:00:28,730
Use the Agent Task Brief on your next assignment.

7
00:00:28,730 --> 00:00:37,557
If the artifact, sources, constraints, review, format, or handoff is vague, repair that field before giving the agent more tools or authority.

8
00:00:37,557 --> 00:00:39,403
Follow Tiny Agent.

9
00:00:39,403 --> 00:00:42,442
Tiny Agent helps you get better at using AI.
